    <sec id="Sec6">
      <title>Selection of multiple reference samples</title>
      <p id="Par61">Suppose the RNA-seq samples are indexed by <inline-formula id="IEq64"><alternatives><tex-math id="M139">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
