      <p id="Par65">To understand the rationale of the model (<xref rid="Equ3" ref-type="">3</xref>), we consider the specific situation in which the scaling coefficients of the read counts from different samples are at the same level. Now it suffices to consider the single-parameter case where <inline-formula id="IEq82"><alternatives><tex-math id="M177">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
